Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想讓大家盡興而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幢別墅曾經屬於我岳父
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你明知如此而惡意侮辱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不輕饒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖是真有所不知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是個奇妙的巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您對此處是瞭如指掌 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場遊戲 一開始就不甚公平
