Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正打算把獎品的盒子交給維多利亞夫人時就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:04:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是貧血吧 無甚大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再問一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若真的知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就回答我
