Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 貝爾圖喬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個印記…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要硬撐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說您也不會聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願意跟隨我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到地獄的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 無論去哪兒我都伴您左右
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「巖窟王」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「巖窟王」…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的事 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自作主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了無禮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆能平常地交談了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…誤解了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能好好交流 真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…一放鬆下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝先生 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺心中的石頭放下了一般
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是特別為您調製的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治療胸口疼痛是最有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您操心了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何就突然感到不適
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝那傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可從小就沒怎麼病過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲先生和阿爾貝先生是青梅竹馬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜小姐告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你們兩人一直很要好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也很羨慕你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我和他認識很久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是時間長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人之間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有著別人無法介入的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 您是從什麼時候起對瓦朗蒂娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被其未婚夫問起這個 真讓人困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 是在下的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡就是喜歡 有什麼不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您又說這種不負責任的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不負責任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼您不愛瓦朗蒂娜小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那您呢 不能結婚就會放棄愛她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不能與之結合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非您也有無法實現的戀情？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚並不是給對方幸福的唯一途徑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 或許真是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜真是幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:11:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒昧問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您今天吃過些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒時間 所以什麼也沒吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝過擺著藍花的桌上的水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的花 那是維爾福家坐的桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝 冷靜聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您身體不適的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東方宇宙被稱為「鴆毒」的可怕毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那水裡有毒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰塊融化稀釋了毒 您才化險為夷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真的是千鈞一髮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標可能並不是您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是往那個水瓶裡下的毒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標應該是維爾福家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂他人的憎恨與嫉妒之心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在本人無從預知之處悄然滋長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人越是幸福 就越…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是以未遂告終
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下一個陷阱將會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望那家有人能獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還是靜養一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 阿爾貝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 必須趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容後再說明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 趕快去找瓦朗蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去瓦朗蒂娜小姐那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真是個可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而是又那樣的迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎 波畢魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動用一切網絡 調查那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是馬賽 要重點調查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼基督山伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻就剝下你的畫皮來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:15:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首席檢察官大人和那個男的是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些你不用管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠什麼的 您多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖父您看 很漂亮的念珠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fs22}rosario：基督教宗教用品，通常由6顆大珠\N53顆小珠和一個小型十字架串成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送飲料來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 巴魯瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此 維爾福家怎會被人盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伯爵想太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲 願意聽我的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 說得這麼見外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你會笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為彼此著想 真的很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 突然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望瓦朗蒂娜和馬克西米利安能得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你的心情會很複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也從心底裡這麼希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能的話 希望兩個彼此傾慕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能共結連理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩人是真愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他們幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能讓什麼毒藥來破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨勢似乎漸強了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 好悶熱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很熱吧 巴魯瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也喝點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴魯瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴魯瓦 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴魯瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴魯瓦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴魯瓦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖…父…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 快去請大夫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…和伯爵說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用問 當然是伯爵那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人說不定會有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論去哪兒我都伴您左右
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「巖窟王」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧 伯爵因公外出了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何時會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都隨伯爵的心情而定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:19:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自一人就一事無成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人期待 今後的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有勇氣去瞭解未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死 瓦朗蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從暗之夢中甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從地底深處復生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悖逆道德之聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛與被愛亦不自知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵蝕日常的黑影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本應死去的舊友寄來的信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 巖窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十幕\N愛德蒙的信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然後期待
